name: Dress For Success San Jose
short_desc: Dress For Success is to promote the economic independence of disadvantaged women by providing professional attire.
description: Dress For Success is to promote the economic independence of disadvantaged women by providing professional attire, a network of support and the career development tools to help women thrive in work and in life. Dress for success serves clients by referral only, and women must have an interview scheduled before receiving clothing.
